author: Chuck Todd and Mark Murray and Carrie Dann and Melissa Holzberg
title: Wisconsin's election clash is a warning for November
description: What’s been playing out as Wisconsin moves ahead with its presidential primary this Tuesday could very well be a harbinger of what might happen in November.
content:
